profile: Located 2km north of Barrie, THAT BACKYARD PLACE is ideally situated to provide design, build and installation services from the GTA to cottage country. We have provided top quality storage solutions, bunkies and garden buildings in Simcoe County, York Region and Muskoka since 2001.  Visit us at www.gazebosheds.com.
